* ===========================================================================
* mm1_validation.gps   --   GPSS World
* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Independent validation model for the Python event-scheduling simulator.
*
* ---- 1. TABELLA DI QUANTILI PER LA DISTRIBUZIONE ESPONENZIALE ----
EXPON    FUNCTION  RN1,C24
0,0/.1,.104/.2,.222/.3,.356/.4,.509/.5,.693/.6,.916/.7,1.2/.75,1.38
.8,1.6/.84,1.83/.88,2.12/.9,2.3/.92,2.52/.94,2.81/.95,2.99/.96,3.2
.97,3.5/.98,3.9/.99,4.6/.995,5.3/.998,6.2/.999,7/.9998,8

* ---- 2. ALLOCAZIONE RISORSE ----
SERVERS  STORAGE   1

         SIMULATE

* ---- 3. DINAMICA DELLE TRANSAZIONI ---------------------------------------
* IAT: lambda = 0.8 -> Media = 1.25. Uso il modificatore di funzione FN$EXPON
         GENERATE  1.25,FN$EXPON
         QUEUE     SYSTEM
         QUEUE     WAIT
         ENTER     SERVERS
         DEPART    WAIT
* ST: mu = 1.0 -> Media = 1.0
         ADVANCE   1.0,FN$EXPON
         LEAVE     SERVERS
         DEPART    SYSTEM
         TERMINATE

* ---- 4. CONTROLLO TEMPO DI RUN -------------------------------------------
         GENERATE  50000
         TERMINATE 1
         START     1
